Evaluate Weapon - information skill
------------------------------------------------------------
Swashbucklers are well trained in the lore of weapons,
including those weapons which they themselves choose not to
use, such as polearms. They may call upon this knowledge in
order to evaluate a weapon. Aside from anaccurate evaluation
of the weapon's strength, some additional information may be
gleaned, such as whether the weapon is unique, whether it
causes a special effect when it strikes, and so on. It will
not, however, determine hidden information about a weapon in
the manner an identify spell would; it is still a non-
magical skill, no matter how accurate.

GL:  1
SP:  5
command:  sevaluate <weapon>
duration: instant
